x-sap-shortText: API to access the income tax declaration records and submit tax declarations actuals

info.title: Income Tax Declaration
info.description:
You can use these APIs to record income tax declaration and submit tax declarations actuals. You can also use these APIs to categorize or group investment types, and configure the window period that controls the creation of actuals and proposals.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)
